nce late\n2014 can be explained by an EXor-like outburst, the recovery from a long\nduration eclipse event caused by obscuring circumstellar dust, or by the\ngradual removal of extincting material from along the line of sight. Our\nanalysis here favors one of the extinction scenarios.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Sep 2017 17:37:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-11"}
