ncreases for\nstronger adhesion which means that adhesion controlled friction dominated by\nload controlled friction. We also observe that adhesion increases on a surface\nwith a lower value of roughness.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Sep 2017 09:48:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 21 Sep 2017 11:10:18 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 9 Sep 2018 11:12:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-11"}
