mplemented. Sensitivity studies as\nwell as validation of the model against measured data available in the open\nliterature have been performed and it has been shown that a reasonable\nagreement between predictions and experiments has been achieved.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Sep 2017 11:49:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-07"}
